is in a VMA with a write permission enabled.
I'm using the following machine attributes:
*************************************************************
Host Name         : mtlsqt185
Host Architecture : ppc64
Linux Distribution: SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 10 (ppc) VERSION = 10 
