/tmp/tsscr/svn.mlx_tp/branches/ofed1.2.5/gen2/userspace/useraccess/gen2_basic/gen2_basic 
1005e000-1015f000 rw-p 1005e000 00:00 0                                  
[heap]
Is this is a security hole (any virus can change the code in the code 
segment ...)
